The paper deals with a reinforcement learning problem with a known state transition model, which is a common topic in the field of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of deep recurrent neural networks (RNNs) and Monte Carlo Tree Search (MCTS) also suggests that the paper may fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), natural language processing (cs.CL), and deep learning (cs.DL). Additionally, the application of the proposed algorithm to knowledge base completion (KBC) implies that the paper may also belong to the information retrieval (cs.IR) category.
